          "text": "This is the Gemini CLI. We are setting up the context for our chat.\nToday's date is Saturday, January 31, 2026 (formatted according to the user's locale).\nMy operating system is: darwin\nThe project's temporary directory is: /Users/gsung/.gemini/tmp/dfb076009187cc63ff44353f89bc091afbed571b40c95a1c54a5d427fe5663c7\nI'm currently working in the directory: /Users/gsung/MyCode/georgesung.github.io\nHere is the folder structure of the current working directories:\n\nShowing up to 200 items (files + folders). Folders or files indicated with ... contain more items not shown, were ignored, or the display limit (200 items) was reached.\n\n/Users/gsung/MyCode/georgesung.github.io/\n├───_config.yml\n├───.gitignore\n├───404.html\n├───about.markdown\n├───CNAME\n├───favicon.svg\n├───Gemfile\n├───Gemfile.lock\n├───index.markdown\n├───_includes/\n│   └───head.html\n├───_layouts/\n│   └───post.html\n├───_posts/\n│   ├───2023-04-22-autogpt-arch.md\n│   ├───2023-05-06-llm-qa-eval-wikipedia.md\n│   └───2023-07-02-qlora-ift.md\n├───.git/...\n└───assets/\n    └───img/\n        ├───auto_gpt.svg\n        ├───profile_photo.png\n        ├───wikiqa_guardrail.svg\n        ├───wikiqa_qa.svg\n        └───wikiqa_search.svg\n\nReminder: Do not return an empty response when a tool call is required.\n\nMy setup is complete. I will provide my first command in the next turn."
